snippet.title: Trailer Sea Bubble. KST Studio. Indie game dev
snippet.description:
Add the game to wish list:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1103310/Sea_Bubble/

Sea Bubble is our first released project, an arcade two-player competitive videogame.

This beautifully well-crafted trailer was made by our Marketing, Event and Community Manager and Content Creator Angie Varela.

Music: In the Hall of the Mountain King by Edvard Grieg.

(@kst_studio_) https://twitter.com/kst_studio

strangetable.mkt@gmail.com
